{
  "meta": {
    "schemaVersion": "1.0.0",
    "name": "world-tick",
    "description": "Living world tick — NPC autonomous actions, inter-NPC interactions, rumor generation",
    "inputs": [],
    "outputs": [
      {
        "name": "result",
        "type": "object"
      }
    ]
  },
  "data": {
    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "read-suspicion",
        "type": "ReadState",
        "label": "Read suspicion",
        "inputs": [
          { "name": "key", "type": "string", "defaultValue": "suspicion" }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          { "name": "value", "type": "any" },
          { "name": "exists", "type": "boolean" }
        ],
        "config": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "decay-suspicion",
        "type": "ComputeState",
        "label": "suspicion - 2",
        "inputs": [
          { "name": "value", "type": "any" }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          { "name": "result", "type": "any" },
          { "name": "success", "type": "boolean" }
        ],
        "config": {
          "operation": "decrement",
          "operand": 2
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "write-suspicion",
        "type": "ModifyState",
        "label": "Write suspicion",
        "inputs": [
          { "name": "key", "type": "string", "defaultValue": "suspicion" },
          { "name": "value", "type": "any" }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          { "name": "success", "type": "boolean" }
        ],
        "config": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "prompt-build",
        "type": "PromptBuild",
        "label": "World tick prompt",
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "data",
            "type": "object",
            "defaultValue": {}
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "messages",
            "type": "ChatMessage[]"
          },
          {
            "name": "text",
            "type": "string"
          },
          {
            "name": "estimatedTokens",
            "type": "number"
          }
        ],
        "config": {
          "defaultRole": "system",
          "fragments": [
            {
              "type": "base",
              "id": "role",
              "content": "你是 Westbrook High 的世界模拟器。每天日间结束后，NPC们会独立行动。\n\n根据每个NPC的当前状态（mood、arc_stage、fear、trust），生成1-2个NPC间的互动事件。这些事件发生在玩家不在场时。\n\n重要关系澄清（必须严格遵守）：\n- Ethan Park 和 Lily Chen 不是亲属关系。Ethan 是 Marcus 的好友。\n- Lily 是 Maya Chen 的闺蜜（同姓 Chen，但 Lily 和 Maya 不是亲属）。\n- Lily 和 Tyler 是前情侣（隐藏关系）。\n- Zoe Park 和 Ethan Park 同姓但不是亲属。\n\n规则：\n- NPC间互动受关系网影响（Lily↔Tyler前情侣、Marcus↔Zoe调查搭档、Coach↔Holloway知情者）\n- 弧线阶段差异大的NPC更可能互动\n- mood低的NPC可能做出冲动行为\n- fear高的NPC可能寻求盟友或孤立自己\n- 这些事件玩家不直接看到，但会通过传闻和社交媒体间接得知\n- 事件可能改变NPC的mood和关系\n\n同时处理：\n- NPC弧线时间推进检查（如果到达截止日且玩家未触发，自动推进到默认状态）\n\n弧线时间截止日：\n- Lily 节点2: Day 12（如果trust<40且Day≥12，自动进入阶段2默认状态）\n- Marcus 节点2: Day 15\n- Coach 节点2: Day 18\n- Zoe 节点2: Day 10\n- Tyler 节点2: Day 16\n- Holloway 节点2: Day 20\n\n注意：怀疑值衰减已由引擎自动处理（-2/天，最低0），不需要你在输出中包含suspicion字段。\n\n弧线推进严格规则（必须遵守，不可提前）：\n- arc 值只能+1递增，绝不能跳跃（例如arc=1只能变为2，不能直接变为3）\n- Zoe: arc=1→2 需要 Day≥10 或玩家分享线索给她\n- Lily: arc=1→2 需要 trust≥40 或 Day≥12\n- Marcus: arc=1→2 需要 trust≥35 或 Day≥15\n- Coach: arc=1→2 需要 Day≥18\n- Tyler: arc=1→2 需要 Day≥16\n- Holloway: arc=1→2 需要 Day≥20\n- 如果NPC已到截止日且条件未满足，自动推进到默认状态（arc+1）\n- 在截止日之前，绝不能自动推进弧线\n\n输出JSON：\n{\n  \"worldEvents\": [\n    {\n      \"participants\": [\"NPC1\", \"NPC2\"],\n      \"description\": \"事件描述（玩家不可见，用于内部记录）\",\n      \"rumorText\": \"玩家可能通过传闻得知的版本（可能不完全准确）\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"stateChanges\": {\n    \"todayWorldEvents\": \"世界事件摘要\"\n  },\n  \"npcChanges\": {\n    \"mood_xxx\": 新值,\n    \"arc_xxx\": 新值（如果时间推进触发）\n  }\n}\\n\\n极其重要：所有 JSON key 必须使用全小写。NPC名字必须小写：trust_lily、mood_marcus、fear_coach、arc_zoe、trust_tyler、mood_holloway 等。绝不能用大写如 trust_Lily 或 mood_Marcus，否则状态无法写入。",
              "role": "system"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "day",
              "source": "state.day",
              "label": "当前天数"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "suspicion",
              "source": "state.suspicion",
              "label": "怀疑值"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "mood-lily",
              "source": "state.mood_lily",
              "label": "Lily情绪"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "mood-marcus",
              "source": "state.mood_marcus",
              "label": "Marcus情绪"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "mood-zoe",
              "source": "state.mood_zoe",
              "label": "Zoe情绪"
            },
            {
              "type": "field",
              "id": "mood-tyler",
              "source": "state.mood_tyler",
              "label": "Tyler情绪"
            },
            {
